* Iron Raptor ignored Liono and his little comments.
At that moment she couldn't even belive that she had listened to him if this 
was his true self. Some man who got in a hissy fit just because something 
didn't go his way.
She didn't hate him but she wouldn't let this go. At least Angel Prime had 
appologized. This man was just plain rude.
< I'll get you back. One way or another.>
Iron Raptor growled and narroewd her eyes.< Same with the Alliance. One way 
or another.....> Her fist clenched and she clamped her jaw.
She hated this! Waiting like some dog ready to serve it's master. But she 
had to wait, just a little longer.*
